ge": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593049}, {"id": 73996, "content": "工作都一样，都是为别人的利益卖力而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594025}, {"id": 227853, "content": "以学习的名义工作，却是在打杂，并且拿最低工资，最后什么都没学到。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 373938}, {"id": 74515, "content": "生病了想请假，领导说，生病？我怎么就不会呢？多喝水吧，大家都在忙呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594970}, {"id": 74007, "content": "做设计，每天没事也要加班，上班时间完全黑白颠倒", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543482}, {"id": 74008, "content": "虽然工作了 但无事可做 事业单位的苦！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338708}, {"id": 74264, "content": "糟糕的工作让你没有选择权", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 74009, "content": "工资低的工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258066}, {"id": 74011, "content": "参加空乘，都到体检了就因为一个看不出来的外科问题把我刷掉了。也不发个短信或者电话告知一下。还要自己打电话去确认。体检费自理机票自理住宿自理。吐血", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595231}, {"id": 79132, "content": "钱少事多离家远！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611223}, {"id": 74013, "content": "招商银行 对公柜员 每天跟机器人一样做事，回家准备考试，365天无休", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595238}, {"id": 74014, "content": "领导不和，我们小的受苦，做了一个月就不做了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593531}, {"id": 74016, "content": "我想好好干 领导却捣乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513104}, {"id": 74017, "content": "拿实习生的工资，干正式员工的活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549626}, {"id": 75297, "content": "压制自己的个人发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571350}, {"id": 74018, "content": "做视频后期，这岗位全公司就我一个，每天累成狗还不招人更不能请假", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508286}, {"id": 74020, "content": "没事情做 没人教你怎么做", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591842}, {"id": 74021, "content": "自己当坏人，他却装的跟个傻逼一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595255}, {"id": 74022, "content": "，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595255}, {"id": 74023, "content": "额", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595255}, {"id": 74025, "content": "说好给2000 最后给1000理由是这要扣那要扣  反正不想", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585466}, {"id": 74027, "content": "电视台主持人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 74028, "content": "画了一张巨大的饼，然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595277}, {"id": 74286, "content": "老板的激励都是阶级资本主义在忽悠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596404}, {"id": 74542, "content": "今天应聘一份文职工作，公司一个一个轮流着来面试，问着一样的问题。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226965}, {"id": 84782, "content": "老板不能公私分明，财务管理混乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634548}, {"id": 74032, "content": "公司太垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511323}, {"id": 74033, "content": "进入公司几个礼拜，公司每一人都拿自己当空气", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591661}, {"id": 74034, "content": "你已经做的很好了 我用了另一个的设计方案", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318585}, {"id": 74035, "content": "做的是暖通设计的工作，天天被老板逼着加班搞广告P图。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579167}, {"id": 74293, "content": "面对无数个智障", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508921}, {"id": 74038, "content": "明明老板这样做不对，或者效果不好，效率不高，但还得做", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285764}, {"id": 74039, "content": "有限的知识遇到无限的问题，poor", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 74040, "content": "第一份工作。校招进的，让我知道了资本家真的只需要剥削剩余价值。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294553}, {"id": 74041, "content": "不是财务但是却贴发票贴了一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43355}, {"id": 74042, "content": "不知道啥工作，干半天离职了。领导让出差去外地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 76346, "content": "忘记约了今天的面试", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288014}, {"id": 74045, "content": "领导衰 衰一窝", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573498}]}